---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About - Majid Babaeifar"
  description="Learn more about Majid Babaeifar, a full-stack software engineer with 7+ years of experience building scalable applications."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">About Me</h1>

    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p class="text-xl text-[var(--color-text-light)] leading-relaxed mb-8">
        I'm a software engineer with over 7 years of professional experience, having built software serving millions of users, successfully launched MVPs, and led teams of engineers.
      </p>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Current Role</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          I currently work as a <strong>Software Developer at EmpirieCom</strong> in Bavaria, Germany (remote),
          where I build full-stack solutions for high-demand e-commerce platforms including Otto, Baur, and other major European brands.
        </p>
        <p>
          My work focuses on backend services powering product detail pages with extremely low latency and high availability,
          using technologies like <strong>Java (Quarkus)</strong>, <strong>TypeScript (Next.js)</strong>, <strong>PostgreSQL</strong>,
          and <strong>Kafka</strong> in cloud-native environments.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Experience Highlights</h2>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">EmpirieCom (2024 - Present)</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-[var(--color-text-light)]">
              <li>Designed and maintained backend services for high-traffic product detail pages</li>
              <li>Migrated legacy key-value store to modern relational data model</li>
              <li>Implemented centralized observability using Grafana and Prometheus</li>
              <li>Optimized database schemas for high-throughput workloads</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Rovren (2023 - 2024)</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-[var(--color-text-light)]">
              <li>Built SaaS platform for image processing using OpenCV</li>
              <li>Implemented dynamic Python code generation from visual workflows</li>
              <li>Developed responsive, SEO-friendly multilingual landing pages</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Iran Insurance (2022 - 2023)</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-[var(--color-text-light)]">
              <li>Rebuilt national insurance website as Progressive Web App (PWA)</li>
              <li>Served 30+ million users with micro-frontend architecture</li>
              <li>Led and mentored team of junior developers</li>
              <li>Enhanced security to meet OWASP standards</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Technical Skills</h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Languages</h3>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-text-light)]">Java, JavaScript, TypeScript, SQL, F#</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Frameworks</h3>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-text-light)]">Quarkus, Next.js, React, Node.js, Express, Spring Boot</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Data & Messaging</h3>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-text-light)]">PostgreSQL, Kafka, MongoDB, MySQL</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">DevOps & Cloud</h3>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-text-light)]">Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD, Nginx, Google Cloud</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Education</h2>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold">M.Sc. International Software Systems Science</h3>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-text-light)]">Otto-Friedrich University Bamberg, Germany (2024-2025)</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-light)] mt-2">
              Master's thesis on BLECH compiler, extending support for policy-based scheduling
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold">B.Sc. Software Computer Engineering</h3>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-text-light)]">Azad University, Tehran (2019-2021)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">What I Value</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-[var(--color-text-light)]">
          <li><strong>Tests & Linters</strong> - Code quality is non-negotiable</li>
          <li><strong>Automation</strong> - If you do it twice, automate it</li>
          <li><strong>Architecture & Design</strong> - Build systems that last</li>
          <li><strong>Optimization</strong> - Performance matters</li>
          <li><strong>Teamwork</strong> - Great software is built by great teams</li>
          <li><strong>Documentation</strong> - Code is read more than it's written</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Beyond Code</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-light)]">
          When I'm not coding, you'll find me hiking in the Bavarian countryside, watching movies,
          listening to music, reading, or having meaningful conversations about technology, life, and everything in between.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-[var(--color-border)]">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Let's Connect</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          I'm always interested in connecting with fellow developers, discussing technology,
          or exploring collaboration opportunities.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="mailto:majidbabaeifar@gmail.com" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-[var(--color-accent)] text-white rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-accent-hover)] transition-colors">
            Email Me
          </a>
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/majidbabaeifar" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 border-2 border-[var(--color-accent)] text-[var(--color-accent)] rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-accent)] hover:text-white transition-colors">
            LinkedIn
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/majidbabaeifar" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 border-2 border-[var(--color-accent)] text-[var(--color-accent)] rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-accent)] hover:text-white transition-colors">
            GitHub
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
